                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">The authoritative, comprehensive guide to Southern California's most popular desert park, much of it still wilderness. A great guide for hikers, off-road travelers, equestrians, mountain bikers, photographers, and campers. Comes with folded 4-color map.</span>
              
